-- Cairn Energy in Talks with Indian Government on Vedanta Purchase, ET Says
-- B y   V   R a m a k r i s h n a n
-- 2010-10-11T01:35:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/cairn-energy-in-talks-with-indian-government-on-vedanta-purchase-et-says.html
Cairn Energy Plc is in talks with
the Indian government and Oil and Natural Gas Corp. over its
plan to sell its unit to Vedanta Resources Plc and is hopeful
that the transaction will be approved soon, Chief Executive
Officer Bill Gammell said, according to the Economic Times.  To contact the reporter on this story:
